  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0dda \u0db8\u0dd6\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dae\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd8\u0dad \u0d9a\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The headquarters of the New Lanka Freedom Party will be opened",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The opening of the party headquarters of the 'New Lanka Freedom Party' chaired by Member of Parliament Kumara Welgama was done in Battaramulla today (05) in the morning under the chairmanship of Mrs. Chandrika Bandaranaike Kumaratunga.",
        "While congratulating the new party chaired by Mr. Kumara Welgama, former President Mrs. Chandrika Bandaranaike said that if this party wants to go a long way, only people who think of a corruption-free country should be added to it.",
        "Leader of the 43rd Division, Member of Parliament Patali Champika Ranawaka, Independent Members of Parliament Anura Priyadarshana Yapa, Chandima Weerakkodi and others were present on this occasion.",
        "Former Minister Jeevan Kumaranatunga is the Deputy Chairman of the New Lanka Freedom Party and the General Secretary is Mr. Tilak Varagoda, a former member of the Provincial Council.",
        "Speaking here, Mr. Kumara Welgama said that more people are ready to join this party in the future."
      ],
